    When did S22 come out?
    25 February 2022
    The three phones were released in the United States and Europe on 25 February 2022. The Galaxy S22, S22+, and S22 Ultra launch with prices at $799.99, $999.99, and $1199.99, respectively. It was succeeded by the Samsung Galaxy S23.
